      <p>Hi!  Just wondering if the greens can be made a day ahead and reheated?  I&#39;ve recently discovered how fabulous winter greens are and am thinking they would make a great Thanksgiving side dish, but try to do the least amount of cooking possible on actual Turkey day.</p>
